data.description: This 3 bedroom 1 bath home features a large back yard and beautiful hardwood floors. Two bedrooms are upstairs with closets and the stairway has been carpeted. A master bedroom and Dining room have a walk-in closet with a new floor. Privacy fence has been newly built and a new handrail has been installed. The large back yard comes equipped with a large brick patio and pergola. Home is close to two parks and a walking trail. Must see it!!!
